        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 4 at 2:16AM EDT by NWS Upton NY</headline>
        <description>Recent dry weather, combined with south winds gusting to 20 to 25
mph and relative humidity as low as 40 percent, may make
conditions more favorable for fire growth and spread today,
mainly during the afternoon. Any fires that develop may be harder
to contain.
